{"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"metadata":{"role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"roleHeading":"Enumeration Case","externalID":"c:@E@MLNTextWritingMode@MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal","symbolKind":"case","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal"}],"title":"MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal"},"sections":[],"kind":"symbol","variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlntextwritingmode\/mlntextwritingmodehorizontal"]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTextWritingMode"]]},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"If a text’s language supports horizontal writing mode, symbols with point"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"placement would be laid out horizontally."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS","iPadOS","Mac Catalyst"],"tokens":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal"}],"languages":["occ"]}]}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTextWritingMode\/MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNTextWritingMode/MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal":{"title":"MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal","role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlntextwritingmode\/mlntextwritingmodehorizontal","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"If a text’s language supports horizontal writing mode, symbols with point"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"placement would be laid out horizontally."}],"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTextWritingMode\/MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","title":"MapLibre","type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling.","type":"text"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","role":"collection","kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNTextWritingMode":{"title":"MLNTextWritingMode","role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlntextwritingmode","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The property allows control over a symbol’s orientation. Note that the property"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"values act as a hint, so that a symbol whose language doesn’t support the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"provided orientation will be laid out in its natural orientation. Example:"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"English point symbol will be rendered horizontally even if array value contains"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"single ‘vertical’ enum value. The order of elements in an array define priority"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"order for the placement of an orientation variant."}],"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNTextWritingMode"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTextWritingMode"}}}